&lt;h1 id="groups-never-admit-failure"&gt;Groups Never Admit Failure&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Dec 8 2021&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You get a schism instead&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Naval:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;
Groups never admit failure. A group would rather keep living in the mythology of &amp;ldquo;we were repressed&amp;rdquo; than ever admit failure. Individuals are the only ones who admit failure. Even individuals don&amp;rsquo;t like to admit failure, but eventually, they can be forced to.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>